<emphasis bold="true" box="[403,612,1636,1660]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">Schistocerca cohni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[620,679,1636,1659]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
holotype dorsal view (A), holotype lateral view (B), “basal eminence” of zygoma (C), ectophallic sclerite (D), cingulum (E), epiphallus (F), endophallus (G), male epiproct (H), male subgenital plate (I), and male cercus (J).
</paragraph>
